name: Five Things to Do with an Entenmann's All Butter Loaf Cake
description: Entenmann's is a ubiquitous part of drugstore and supermarket displays. My all-time favorite item is the All Butter Loaf. The ever-so-soft moistness, the eerily golden brown top, and the loaf ends--so delicious. Here are five simple ways to use the cake as a base for other more exciting and impressive-looking preparations.
